{"tid":1392612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲搞ocamp係咪痴撚線","createTime":"2019-07-31T20:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T20:54:52.000Z","uid":77872,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc59e1c8891ee6c4b9c84d1bc58d1341f3a82611","tid":1392612,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"香港嚟個風頭火勢你班大學生仲要用咁多人力物力搞啲ocamp，詳細分析如下<br />\n<br />\n[簡單分析大學戰線]學生會同屬會要盡快有共識罷搞O camp<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392551</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n風平浪靜我真係理撚得你，香港依家出撚曬事啦，如果到時又要人，係咪又話要籌備又話參加緊啲乜ocamp所以唔去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞又要錢又要人力，參加嗰啲又要比錢又要時間，至少都留你一晚，有啲甚至留你十日，冇錯係十日啊大佬，咪話十日啊，依家一日都世界大變啦。與其搞ocamp，不如閒日叫啲大學生出街做多啲宣傳，大學生其中一個又是就係時間多，但係啲時間唔好曬咗佢啦"},{"pid":"24c30f6ae960c6b82e0515cb6b0dc031a6f5ee28","tid":1392612,"uid":142233,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:48:27.000Z","msg":"俾佢地自主決定啦 我覺得無所謂 適當時候歸隊就得"},{"pid":"04c1006de2eb6d21b4cd0702ed05d4e334ca052b","tid":1392612,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:54:27.000Z","msg":"Ocamp 組織返啲人一齊出嚟發夢都ok<br />\n<br />\n關鍵應景唔在於搞啲咩，而係點搞，同埋有咩人搞"},{"pid":"be9f9d0f08152f0644c7265c03101549fc87b34d","tid":1392612,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dubRXdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdubRXdk.jpg&h=a56247f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲花大量時間搞ocamp，我諗好多香港人都會對你地好失望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}